# ShopNest E-commerce Dashboard (Power BI)

## 📊 Project Overview
This project analyzes e-commerce sales data using Power BI to generate insights on revenue, customer behavior, delivery performance, and product ratings.

## 🔧 Tools & Technologies
- Power BI
- DAX
- Data Modeling
- Power Query

## 📈 Key Features
- KPI Cards (Revenue, Orders, Delayed Orders, Rating)
- Top & Bottom Rated Products
- Payment Method Analysis
- Monthly, Quarterly & Yearly Trends
- State-wise Sales Analysis

## 📌 Insights
- Credit card is the most used payment method
- Certain categories contribute highest revenue
- Delayed deliveries peak in specific months
